ugin developed and provided by <a href="http://developers.facebook.com">Facebook Developers</a>. Detailed information on the plugin can be found at <a href="http://developers.facebook.com/docs/reference/plugins/comments/">http://developers.facebook.com/docs/reference/plugins/comments/</a>.', 'd9a2538f-142d-44ec-9b30-5231a008e7bf', '20120913 13:56:34', 0, 0, N'<form></form>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '8888245a-c384-40ec-bc97-6ddcea91ef68')
